{"tid":412070,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"[悠二評測]ASUS ROG Strix RX VEGA64 OC 8GB 評測","createTime":"2017-09-24T10:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T15:42:21.000Z","uid":14049,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4bc77cedbb852ab0adf20ba68bbc8b051fc325da","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"全球第一個非公Vega 64降壓測試?<br />\n<br />\n今次呢張卡研究左好耐，好難玩<br />\n<br />\n不過終於都測試完畢<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://yujihw.com/review/asus-rog-strix-rx-vega64-oc-edition-8gb-hbm2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2Freview%2Fasus-rog-strix-rx-vega64-oc-edition-8gb-hbm2&d=SmmKGvdAKZkurWpwob5GVwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=3c07e66a\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/review/asus-rog-strix-rx-vega64-oc-edition-8gb-hbm2</a>"},{"pid":"ad4e4eb300d3e79e63caa05449818591ba0b20db","tid":412070,"uid":22817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:03:13.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"33f16688acdbb514d2367ddb879f5cac8918e520","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:34:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Lm</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb797f13c8eb0a0cc023b37d9ecc0ccf83f1f2c","tid":412070,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:05:52.000Z","msg":"羅拉dx11,dx12 fps差成倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw d打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eaaf8706b5d43233eebeb3c429c4b62a1141ed24","tid":412070,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"電壓set得咁高都唔知係amd保守定nv太激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc257760a3e728595b13989abb3e4d15db571603","tid":412070,"uid":47999,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:09:06.000Z","msg":"詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c6a34ed385fca3b0db8ae5fb53fd0d142ed313c","tid":412070,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab26b3892a6de75accb36fef500d7652fbb4905f","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:27:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅拉dx11,dx12 fps差成倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw d打燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我仲未得閒搞燈箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eaa42848fd446a3c86f51c84e8f7f8e008ed090","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:28:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詳盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我有諗過打唔打咁詳盡<br />\n<br />\n因為我驚太詳盡冇乜人會睇咁多字<br />\n<br />\n但呢張卡.我又覺得真係要打咁多.先係值得睇既評測"},{"pid":"79051a867c9f43a0102c7ba40a63e8ff99883b5e","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"其實呢張卡d測試好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n我有跑分同遊戲測試.我有機會會再重新測一次<br />\n<br />\n用另一個平台再測"},{"pid":"e21611c2648fc29f3b5112114528793b6a733c6c","tid":412070,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:32:21.000Z","msg":"好詳盡,不過D中文麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,好多句子要睇多幾次先大概get到"},{"pid":"5df131e827c5ebffc5fbee6a96ca03119fea9f6f","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好詳盡,不過D中文麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,好多句子要睇多幾次先大概get到</blockquote><br />\n打太多次.打打下都唔知打緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過下次會改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8eb26830bd696bfbd510edb16b87ac2e7d69651","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:43:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好詳盡,不過D中文麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,好多句子要睇多幾次先大概get到</blockquote><br />\n打太多<span style=\"color: red;\">字</span>.打打下都唔知打緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過下次會改進<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"5917e53fb76d758839ffc08d1e30e402e29bd221","tid":412070,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T13:59:41.000Z","msg":"點解降壓會勁過stock?<br />\n係咪其實成個test 都throttle緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUV,stock,OC測試途中各自既core clock係點?<br />\n有無stock setting下wattman既畫面?"},{"pid":"94be63788811fbd94e182cad2961b6b1513be1ec","tid":412070,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解降壓會勁過stock?<br />\n係咪其實成個test 都throttle緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUV,stock,OC測試途中各自既core clock係點?<br />\n有無stock setting下wattman既畫面?</blockquote><br />\nStock 會係咁撞power wall, keep唔到peak clock（就算加左power limit)<br />\n<br />\nUV 令佢功耗大降，反而令佢冇咁易撞牆，更加易keep高頻，就算加埋power limit都仲慳電過stock<br />\n<br />\n呢個係公板嘅uv test result"},{"pid":"59a8cbd17b82c2252129bacdc4749d5815fd77ee","tid":412070,"uid":63053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:18:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>點解降壓會勁過stock?<br />\n係咪其實成個test 都throttle緊?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nUV,stock,OC測試途中各自既core clock係點?<br />\n有無stock setting下wattman既畫面?</blockquote><br />\nStock 會係咁撞power wall, keep唔到peak clock（就算加左power limit)<br />\n<br />\nUV 令佢功耗大降，反而令佢冇咁易撞牆，更加易keep高頻，就算加埋power limit都仲慳電過stock<br />\n<br />\n呢個係公板嘅uv test result</blockquote><br />\n簡單D講即係stock setting throttle緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我就問UV test緊既core clock係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bd505888a42bd5728be41c3e96c7f482345c654","tid":412070,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:19:05.000Z","msg":"Btw 日系cap應該好過台系<br />\n點解牙石係都要堆台cap,係咪因該自己公司？"},{"pid":"775bf97ca894c95ded28eaf4df4e1351bd713d2f","tid":412070,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:27:27.000Z","msg":"內容好好不過D相好似影得麻麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你用咩機影? 頭頁果D 好朦下, 同埋打燈唔平均睇得好辛苦"},{"pid":"0159f36571ae82197bbdd94bc6bc4a4376d1f783","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:28:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 日系cap應該好過台系<br />\n點解牙石係都要堆台cap,係咪因該自己公司？</blockquote><br />\n日本仔基本上一定好過台仔<br />\n<br />\n而Asus會用台仔既原因係因為鈺邦呢間野ASUS係股東之一，而且份股係唔細<br />\n<br />\n所以你見asus好多高階板同卡都係用鈺邦<br />\n<br />\n除非商業因素,諗唔到有乜原因係唔用日本仔而係用鈺邦"},{"pid":"3f2b0a4afc1d867ab9084c4c9c24c6fd65740228","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:29:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內容好好不過D相好似影得麻麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你用咩機影? 頭頁果D 好朦下, 同埋打燈唔平均睇得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n只係用緊電話影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燈箱會準備有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇計....資源不足既情況下.唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都準備會引入多D器材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做評測.我係冇錢收的,純粹係興趣而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05de39fe95e6a34bd8357ac10db513c63749adfe","tid":412070,"uid":14049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:31:21.000Z","msg":"公版VEGA 64降壓成績唔錯...<br />\n<br />\n但呢張ASUS 非公....降壓後跑分就勁.實際打機反而唔太掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最唔能夠理解係超頻後.成績下降得好多<br />\n<br />\n只能夠想像呢張卡個Bios有問題.或者我測試既driver都有問題"},{"pid":"61ba2810aa6a6882963ba56cde0f8e7756d0feca","tid":412070,"uid":5771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:38:56.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19873408023bc9448b4d9ff2461d1bedee43a2ab","tid":412070,"uid":896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:47:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>內容好好不過D相好似影得麻麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你用咩機影? 頭頁果D 好朦下, 同埋打燈唔平均睇得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n只係用緊電話影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燈箱會準備有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇計....資源不足既情況下.唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都準備會引入多D器材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做評測.我係冇錢收的,純粹係興趣而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔緊要, 一步一步黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw, 你估依張香港開價洗唔洗 6k <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9713e821f995602fe20c1a244c15566433e9f2c","tid":412070,"uid":1327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T14:53:15.000Z","msg":"好詳細 不過有budget 就買番個燈箱同換個相機<br />\n是關d 圖真係麻煩地"},{"pid":"592bba5245cf3345b27c4be7908bffa5b8f23695","tid":412070,"uid":61763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T15:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>內容好好不過D相好似影得麻麻 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你用咩機影? 頭頁果D 好朦下, 同埋打燈唔平均睇得好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n只係用緊電話影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n燈箱會準備有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇計....資源不足既情況下.唯有係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都準備會引入多D器材<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n做評測.我係冇錢收的,純粹係興趣而做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n寫成咁想收錢笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}